COMPILING THE PROGRAMMES;

compiling the ebpf programme:
  clang -O2 -target bpf -c drop_port.c -o drop_port_kern.o

compiling update port programme:
  clang -O2 -target bpf -c drop_port.c -o drop_port_kern.o

RUNNING THE PROGRAMS;

After loading the ebpf programme:
ip link set dev <interface> xdp obj drop_port_kern.o 
/*what ever the interface we want the ebpf programme will be attached.
  for example we can replace the interface with "eth0" or "wlan0" in the above command*/

update port number from userspace:
./update_port 4040


